.TH "mipi_dsi_generic_write" 9 "mipi_dsi_generic_write" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dsi_generic_write \- transmit data using a generic write packet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "ssize_t" mipi_dsi_generic_write
.BI "(struct mipi_dsi_device *dsi "  ","
.BI "const void *payload "  ","
.BI "size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dsi" 12
DSI peripheral device
.IP "payload" 12
buffer containing the payload
.IP "size" 12
size of payload buffer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function will automatically choose the right data type depending on
the payload length.
.SH "RETURN"
The number of bytes transmitted on success or a negative error code
on failure.
